            "question": "What should I bring to my pet\u2019s first visit?",
            "answer": "<p>Bring current vaccination records (rabies is required). Let us know about any health conditions, allergies, or behavioral concerns at check-in.</p>"
          }
        },
        "q4": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Can I stay during the grooming?",
            "answer": "<p>We find that most pets are calmer without their owner present. You\u2019re welcome to wait in our lobby, or we\u2019ll text you when your pet is ready for pickup.</p>"
          }
        },
